ize growth effect is well accounted for\nthrough an effective length scale accounting for the local friction velocity\nand for the local mean shear.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 23:40:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
