tion for the\ncomplement of a convex compact set $E$ when $n\\leq p<\\infty$. If $\\mu_E$\ndenotes this measure, then we show that necessary and sufficient conditions for\nexistence under this setting are exactly the same conditions as in the\nclassical Minkowski problem. We also show that this problem has a unique\nsolution up to translation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 23:58:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
