y corona heating and UV/optical variation\nis quasars are closely associated with magnetic disc turbulence, and the\ninnermost disc turbulence (where corona heating occurs) correlates with the\nslow turbulence at larger radii (where UV/optical emission is produced).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2018 02:21:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2018 01:41:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-28"}
